### **Common Issues and Fixes**

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Webhook returns 401 | Invalid signature | Check `POLAR_WEBHOOK_SECRET` in Convex env |
| Credits not added | Product ID not mapped | Check product ID in `convex/http.ts` matches Polar |
| Subscription not created | Clerk user ID missing | Ensure `clerk_user_id` in customer metadata |
| Duplicate credits | Idempotency not working | Check `polarOrderId` in transaction metadata |
| Monthly renewal not working | Mutation not implemented | See "Pending Implementation" above |

